title: Ekoplaza - Marktstraat
description: Very large supermarket selling a wide variety of products including health food items. This branch of Ecoplaza is The Netherlands largest organic supermarket (912 square meters). Has a variety of vegetarian and vegan food, also some products from the famous "Vegetarian Butcher". Vegan food is not always labelled as vegan, which is quite normal in NL.
streetAddress: Grote Marktstraat 177, Den Haag, South Holland
